About Me

I specialise in iOS development but also bring full stack development and startup experience. I'm comfortable with condensed learning requirements to bridge project skills gaps. I've taught the iOS App developement course at City University London. The iOS community is fantastic and I'm an active member in both the local and international scene.

I perfer to work remotely with a mix of on site but will also take on London based roles within reasonable commute distance. I'm available for part time or full time projects. I'm not interested in permenant roles but I do offer a retainer for long term support.

My rates for full time on site start at £3000/week and for remote part time from £450/day. I will not work for equity.
